metadata.name: Voxel Crazy Head #1
metadata.description: Welcome to the Voxel Crazy Head project! Voxel Crazy Head is a collection of 10 000 NFT unique heads on the Ethereum blockchain. Each NFT from the collection is a key to the metaverse http://Metaspace.game. The voxel head transforms into a digital avatar and you get access to the http://Metaspace.game metaplatform. 12 attributes and 40778090496000 combinations.Each head has a unique DNA code, which will further influence the fate of the character. Join to Discord! Everything is just beginning!
